  "texts": [
    "This suggests that prompted Self-Edit models struggle with editing based on given feedback to medium or hard prompts, stressing the value of a dedicated Edit model.",
    "In addition, we noticed some unexpected behavior when prompting Llama-3.1-Nemotron-70B-Instruct to edit responses based on feedback.",
    "It sometimes starts with a prefix like \"Here's the edited response:\" or \"I'm glad to hear that the response was helpful\".",
    "Further, it occasionally plans what to do based on the feedback or provides multiple alternative edits (when the edited answer is short).",
    "Such behaviors might not be useful to end users who expect straightforward model responses, similar to the responses before applying the edits."
  ],
